<p>
coopist is the first projec we launch using the coopist methodology.
Thanks for stratup-weekend Hong Kong.
How it works?
</p>

<ul>
	<li>Tweet your thoughts about coopist philosophy with the tag #coopist</li>
	<li>Messages comes in from all kinds of social platforms</li>
	<li>Hot ideas will be carried through by a cooperative society</li>
</ul>

<p>
We are not restricted to Twitter!
All social platform will come in.
Just let us know which platform you want most via #coopist tag.
</p>

<p>
Last, well, you guessed it!
<code>coopist.org</code>
is an Co-Op.
</p>
